                    <p class="source" data-uuid="eb107116df01420cb42616366b6bb915">This photograph shows the inauguration of Jefferson Davis as president of the Confederate States of America. The ceremony took place on February 18, 1861. Jefferson had earlier served as U.S. secretary of war and as a senator from Mississippi.</p>
